front.title: •Quietly Observing
front.gametext: Deploy on Aurra Sing. While Aurra is alone at a site, your total ability here = 0. During your move phase, may lose Effect to target an opponent's lightsaber present. Draw destiny. If destiny > 3, Aurra may 'steal' that lightsaber.
front.lore: On her assignment to kill Sharad Hett, Aurra used her patience and cunning to help track down the Jedi Master.
